RACE.RACE_TEXT: PRAIRIE MEADOWS RACE 1 4 1/2F Dirt CR: 69. Maiden Special Weight Purse 43160. FOR REGISTERED STATE BRED MAIDENS, TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 119 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MC COUGAR came away last and quickly advanced along the inside to race off the top flight, had to wait for racing room around the turn, shifted out three to four wide entering the lane, roused forward to challenge SINCERLY MINE for the lead in the final furlong, briefly matched strides then edged away. SINCERELY MINE raced up close in opening stages then engaged WICKED HOT FOOT for the lead, vied two wide around the turn, shook free with a furlong left to run then got denied by the winner in the final sixteenth. WICKED HOT FOOT broke on top and quickly established the lead, vied inside of SINCERLY MINE around the turn, fought back to the eighth pole then gave way. NICE ONE JULIO raced in contention just off the top flight, chased two wide around the turn, came out wider into stretch run and gave way. D D'S LEGACY raced off the early pace, saved ground around the turn, lugged in down the lane and brushed repeatedly against the rail, had no late response. D'S MIC DROP lacked early speed, saved ground around the turn and never threatened.

BIG HEARTED FACTOR vied with the eventual winner around the first turn and battled on into the backstretch, could not match strides past the half mile marker, weakened around the far turn and continued to tire in the drive.
